# Charts Examples in Zolt

## Mermaid diagram

:::mermaid
flowchart LR
  A[Hard edge] -->|Link text| B(Round edge)
  B --> C{Decision}
  C -->|One| D[Result one]
  C -->|Two| E[Result two]
:::

## Basic Chart Container

Simple chart with one graph:

:::chart
:::chart-line {title="Sales Over Time"}
Jan: 100
Feb: 120
Mar: 150
Apr: 180
:::
:::

## Multiple Charts in Container

Several graphs sharing the same space:

:::chart
:::chart-line {title="Revenue"}
2020: 50000
2021: 75000
2022: 100000
2023: 125000
:::

:::chart-bar {title="Expenses"}
2020: 30000
2021: 35000
2022: 40000
2023: 45000
:::
:::

## Chart Types

### Line Chart

:::chart
:::chart-line {title="Monthly Growth"}
Jan: 20
Feb: 35
Mar: 50
Apr: 75
May: 100
:::
:::

### Bar Chart

:::chart
:::chart-bar {title="Product Sales"}
Widget A: 150
Widget B: 200
Widget C: 175
Widget D: 220
:::
:::

### Pie Chart

:::chart
:::chart-pie {title="Market Share"}
Company A: 35
Company B: 25
Company C: 20
Company D: 15
Others: 5
:::
:::

### Area Chart

:::chart
:::chart-area {title="Traffic Over Time"}
Morning: 120
Afternoon: 200
Evening: 180
Night: 50
:::
:::

## Styled Charts

### Custom Color Schemes

:::chart
:::chart-line {color-scheme=cool title="Cool Colors"}
Jan: 10
Feb: 20
Mar: 30
:::

:::chart-line {color-scheme=warm title="Warm Colors"}
Jan: 100
Feb: 200
Mar: 300
:::
:::

### Chart with Legend

:::chart
:::chart-bar {title="Sales by Region" legend=true}
North: 450
South: 320
East: 280
West: 390
:::
:::

### Chart with Grid

:::chart
:::chart-line {title="Detailed View" grid=true}
Jan: 100
Feb: 150
Mar: 200
:::
:::

